  "segments": [
    {
      "speaker": "夜渡",
      "text": "雾港城东侧封锁线全部闭合。\n塔顶警示灯由蓝转红，意味着现实稳定阈值已跌入危险区。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "display_break_lines": [
        1
      ],
      "character_image": "assets/char_夜渡_observe.png",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_battlefield_night.png"
      }
    },
    {
      "speaker": "岚绮",
      "text": "疏散完成，外圈结界只够撑四十分钟。\n凛白，如果你拖太久，整座城会被术式噪声撕开。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "display_break_lines": [
        1
      ],
      "character_image": "assets/char_岚绮_command.png",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_battlefield_night.png"
      }
    },
    {
      "speaker": "凛白",
      "text": "四十分钟足够。\n我只需要把他留在这片场地。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "display_break_lines": [
        1
      ],
      "character_image": "assets/char_凛白_calm.png",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_battlefield_night.png"
      }
    },
    {
      "speaker": "朽阎",
      "text": "留我？\n你们的时代总爱把希望押在一个人身上。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "display_break_lines": [
        1
      ],
      "character_image": "assets/char_朽阎_dominant.png",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_battlefield_night.png"
      }
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜渡",
      "text": "中心广场温度骤降。\n两人的术压在空气里碰撞，像两层看不见的海潮。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "display_break_lines": [
        1
      ],
      "character_image": "assets/char_夜渡_observe.png",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_battlefield_night.png"
      }
    },
    {
      "speaker": "凛白",
      "text": "第一条规则：不让你跨过中轴线。\n第二条规则：你每适应一次，我就改写一次空间参数。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "display_break_lines": [
        1
      ],
      "character_image": "assets/char_凛白_calm.png",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_battlefield_night.png"
      }
    },
    {
      "speaker": "朽阎",
      "text": "很好。\n那我也给你一条规则——你每后退一步，这座城就少一条街。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "display_break_lines": [
        1
      ],
      "character_image": "assets/char_朽阎_dominant.png",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_battlefield_night.png"
      }
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜渡",
      "text": "开战。\n凛白的指尖划过半空，地面像被无形刀锋切成整齐格网。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "display_break_lines": [
        1
      ],
      "character_image": "assets/char_夜渡_observe.png",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_battlefield_night.png"
      }
    },
    {
      "speaker": "岚绮",
      "text": "中区地形正在重排！\n他把广场压成了可控棋盘。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "display_break_lines": [
        1
      ],
      "character_image": "assets/char_岚绮_command.png",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_battlefield_night.png"
      }
    },
    {
      "speaker": "朽阎",
      "text": "漂亮的牢笼。\n可惜，牢笼也是结构，结构就能被我拆。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "display_break_lines": [
        1
      ],
      "character_image": "assets/char_朽阎_dominant.png",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_battlefield_night.png"
      }
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜渡",
      "text": "朽阎抬手，黑红纹路沿切缝反向爬行。\n凛白刚建立的空间网格出现裂纹。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "display_break_lines": [
        1
      ],
      "character_image": "assets/char_夜渡_observe.png",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_battlefield_night.png"
      }
    },
    {
      "speaker": "凛白",
      "text": "这么快就找到节点？\n那就换算法。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "display_break_lines": [
        1
      ],
      "character_image": "assets/char_凛白_calm.png",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_battlefield_night.png"
      }
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜渡",
      "text": "凛白身后浮现三重几何环。\n每一重都在旋转，像把城市坐标重新命名。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "display_break_lines": [
        1
      ],
      "character_image": "assets/char_夜渡_observe.png",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_domain_collision.png",
        "effects": [
          "fade"
        ],
        "fade_ms": 550
      }
    },
    {
      "speaker": "朽阎",
      "text": "你改名字，我改意义。\n坐标可以骗我，代价不会。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "display_break_lines": [
        1
      ],
      "character_image": "assets/char_朽阎_dominant.png",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_domain_collision.png"
      }
    },
    {
      "speaker": "岚绮",
      "text": "警告！外圈结界功率掉到72%。\n他们的每次对撞都在烧城市地基。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "display_break_lines": [
        1
      ],
      "character_image": "assets/char_岚绮_command.png",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_domain_collision.png"
      }
    },
    {
      "speaker": "凛白",
      "text": "夜渡，记录朽阎每次反制前的停顿。\n我要他的适应节奏。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "display_break_lines": [
        1
      ],
      "character_image": "assets/char_凛白_calm.png",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_domain_collision.png"
      }
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜渡",
      "text": "收到。\n第六次反制前，他都会出现0.4秒静止。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "display_break_lines": [
        1
      ],
      "character_image": "assets/char_夜渡_observe.png",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_domain_collision.png"
      }
    },
    {
      "speaker": "朽阎",
      "text": "观察很细。\n但你们有没有想过，那0.4秒是我留给你们的仁慈？",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "display_break_lines": [
        1
      ],
      "character_image": "assets/char_朽阎_dominant.png",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_domain_collision.png"
      }
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜渡",
      "text": "地表猛然塌陷。\n凛白被迫拉高身位，朽阎顺势近身，进入体术距离。",
      "effect": "shake",
      "speed": 18,
      "display_break_lines": [
        1
      ],
      "character_image": "assets/char_夜渡_observe.png",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_domain_collision.png",
        "effects": [
          "shake"
        ],
        "shake_ms": 320,
        "shake_strength": 10
      }
    },
    {
      "speaker": "凛白",
      "text": "你终于不躲在术式后面了。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "character_image": "assets/char_凛白_calm.png",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_domain_collision.png"
      }
    },
    {
      "speaker": "朽阎",
      "text": "真正的杀意，从来不分远近。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "character_image": "assets/char_朽阎_dominant.png",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_domain_collision.png"
      }
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜渡",
      "text": "两人在坍塌边缘连击。\n拳与刃的残影叠在一起，监测镜头几乎全部失焦。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "display_break_lines": [
        1
      ],
      "character_image": "assets/char_夜渡_observe.png",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_domain_collision.png"
      }
    },
    {
      "speaker": "岚绮",
      "text": "凛白左臂术回路过载！\n再这样硬拼，他的空间场会先崩。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "display_break_lines": [
        1
      ],
      "character_image": "assets/char_岚绮_command.png",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_domain_collision.png"
      }
    },
    {
      "speaker": "凛白",
      "text": "所以我不硬拼。\n我在等你的第七次适应。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "display_break_lines": [
        1
      ],
      "character_image": "assets/char_凛白_calm.png",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_domain_collision.png"
      }
    },
    {
      "speaker": "朽阎",
      "text": "第七次？\n你把我当成按节拍行动的机器？",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "display_break_lines": [
        1
      ],
      "character_image": "assets/char_朽阎_dominant.png",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_domain_collision.png"
      }
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜渡",
      "text": "第七次来了。\n朽阎短暂停顿，凛白将三重几何环瞬间反相，整片战场向内折叠。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
